Package blf.parsing

Class HyperledgerSmartContractAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
blf.grammar.BcqlBaseListener
blf.parsing.SemanticAnalyzer
blf.parsing.HyperledgerSmartContractAnalyzer
All Implemented Interfaces:
BcqlListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class HyperledgerSmartContractAnalyzer extends SemanticAnalyzer
HyperledgerSmartContractAnalyzer this class can check whether the SMART CONTRACT statement was used correctly in the manifest. It will check if the selected blockchain is hyperledger and the manifest specifies to start with the current block.
